      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Parts of compasses and ruling pens, consisting of double nibs connected with a screw to adjust the width between the nibs, used for drawing lines in ink.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
